<p><i>Add information about .<a href="/web/20070729231805/http://www.modwiki.net/w/index.php?title=PK4&amp;action=edit" class="new" title="PK4">PK4</a> Files, unpacking them and best using a different folder, which leads us to:</i>
</p>
<div><a href="/web/20070729231805/http://www.modwiki.net/wiki/Image:D3square_25.png" class="image" title="Image:D3square_25.png"><img src="/web/20070729231805im_/http://www.modwiki.net/w/images/2/23/D3square_25.png" alt="Image:D3square_25.png" width="25" height="25" longdesc="/wiki/Image:D3square_25.png" /></a> <b>Note:</b> Doom 3 only: <dl><dd><i>The original Doom 3 declaration files come with a lot of redundant, deprecated and obsolete or nonworking entries so it's recommended that you use <a href="/web/20070729231805/http://www.modwiki.net/wiki/Eutectic%27s_clean_paks" title="Eutectic's clean paks">eutectic's clean paks</a>.</i></dd></dl></div>
